WEBVTT

00:00.467 --> 00:03.235
<i>Previously on "Transformers Prime"...</i>

00:03.304 --> 00:06.154
Few things of value come
without a price.

00:06.223 --> 00:08.852
What is it that you wish in return?

00:08.921 --> 00:13.452
Only to be a Decepticon once again.

00:13.521 --> 00:17.687
Now, what will we be fishing
for today, my liege?

00:17.756 --> 00:21.426
Starscream's true motives.

00:23.865 --> 00:27.637
Ah, the high-and-mighty
Skyquake.

00:27.706 --> 00:30.912
You shall bow to my command.

00:32.281 --> 00:34.217
Symbiosis.

00:34.286 --> 00:37.090
[ laughs evilly ]

00:37.159 --> 00:39.126
<i>I can feel it!</i>

00:40.195 --> 00:41.395
Awkward.

00:41.464 --> 00:44.868
I will allow you
to return to our ranks.

00:44.936 --> 00:48.039
Oh! Thank the Allspark!

00:48.107 --> 00:51.279
[ screams ]

00:53.676 --> 00:56.117
<b>2x25 - Regeneration</b>

00:56.452 --> 00:59.588
<i>You know, I might not be the
first human on Cybertron, </i>

00:59.656 --> 01:02.024
but I can still be the first human
exchange student.

01:02.093 --> 01:04.828
Why didn't you tell us about
the Omega keys before?

01:04.897 --> 01:06.363
You probably didn't notice,

01:06.432 --> 01:09.835
but things have been kind of
intense around here lately.

01:09.904 --> 01:13.240
So, you guys could really be
going home soon, huh?

01:13.309 --> 01:15.443
Don't worry, Raf.
You'll come visit!

01:15.512 --> 01:18.748
Once we get our place set up, he
can bunk with us, right, Bulk?

01:18.817 --> 01:19.749
Uh, Miko?

01:19.818 --> 01:22.485
You are taking me with you, right?

01:22.553 --> 01:25.521
<i>Aren't we getting ahead of
ourselves here?</i>

01:25.589 --> 01:29.558
Not only do we lack any actual
method of reaching Cybertron,

01:29.627 --> 01:34.664
but Starscream now controls the sole
means of our planet's restoration.

01:34.733 --> 01:36.799
As far as we know.

01:36.868 --> 01:39.168
You think Starscream's
rejoined the Cons?

01:39.237 --> 01:42.606
He might've used the Omega
keys to buy back Megatron's favor.

01:42.675 --> 01:43.206
Hmph.

01:43.275 --> 01:46.377
Without first trying to sell
them to the highest bidder?

01:46.446 --> 01:50.515
It wouldn't surprise me if he had
the nerve to contact us and ...

01:50.584 --> 01:52.517
[ beeping ]

01:52.586 --> 01:55.788
- Okay, that's weird.
- Is it Starscream?

01:55.857 --> 01:57.389
[ beeping continues ]

01:57.458 --> 02:03.296
No. It is Dreadwing.
And he wants to meet.

02:06.502 --> 02:09.798
